This program relies on:
  - the X11 libraries
  - the GTK / C++ bindings (libgtkmm, libgdkmm)
  - the glib2 (libglib-2.0)
  - the glib2 / C++ bindings (libglibmm)
  - the C++ signal/slot library (libsigc++)
  - the C++ runtime libraries (libstdc++)
  - the (X)MedCon medical image convertor library (libmdc)
  - the CCMATH library (libccm)
  - the ImageMagick / C++ bindings (libMagickCore, libMagick++)
  - the DCMTK (C++ DICOM Toolkit) (libofstd, liboflog, libdcmdata)

Installation:
  ./configure --prefix=/some/prefix
  make
  make install
